        {
            "title": "滙豐轉而看跌日圓 稱其風險溢價擴大",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 市場擔憂日本政府支出大幅增加以及通膨捲土重來，導致日圓與美元和國債殖利率的傳統聯繫瓦解，這促使滙豐控股策略師改變他們對未來幾個月日圓走勢的預測。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球投資者通常認為日圓匯率與利率差密切相關，當與美國國債的利差收窄時，日圓會獲得支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但近幾個月來，這種模式不再適用。事實上自10月以來，日圓兌美元匯率已下跌約7%——儘管10年期日本國債與美國國債之間的殖利率利差已收窄近60個基點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括Paul Mackel和Joey Chew在內的外匯策略師團隊在年度展望報告中寫道：「二者之間的這個‘楔形’反映了日圓‘風險溢價’的擴大。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8a3f957e-f5be-396d-8cec-4f2cf89e7db3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mRhJtdkKcjfT6mLtFnwKIA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6f9e3939e734aeb7527645890dc98568\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師們指出，在高市早苗去年出任首相之後，導致日圓出現「結構性疲軟」的投資者擔憂包括債務貨幣化、購買力下降、持續通膨和負實際利率。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們目前預測，日圓兌美元匯率到年中將跌至160關口，而非此前他們預期的走強至150關口。他們表示，使情況更加複雜的因素是，如果日圓跌破160，日本當局很可能會干預外匯市場以支撐匯率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題HSBC Warns Yen’s Surging Risk Premium Has Few Easy Fixes</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E8%BD%89%E8%80%8C%E7%9C%8B%E8%B7%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93-%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%B6%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%BA%A2%E5%83%B9%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7-004304408.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 09:54:34",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲央行總裁拉加德稱特朗普關稅威脅令不確定性捲土重來",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 歐洲央行行長拉加德表示，由於特朗普發出新的關稅威脅，不確定性已捲土重來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她在達沃斯世界經濟論壇向CNN表示，美歐之間的信任正受到破壞，並補充說兩地企業目前試圖搞清楚新關稅措施的連鎖反應。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vGXDGOesbVsGEXBNHhrhWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1319e5b61c3ef4d4672a9ae32f457748\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她在周二播出的這次採訪中稱：「比關稅本身更重要的是，我們再次看到不確定性上升——不確定性又回來了」。她把這些威脅形容為「我們以前看過的電影」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普可能對歐洲國家採取的行動，或將挑戰歐洲央行對未來幾年通脹和經濟活動的樂觀預期。面對日益高漲的保護主義，歐元區迄今展現出韌性，但官員們一直強調風險居高不下。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f9266aa0-5946-302f-a9ed-7fa7359151f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德表示，歐洲的政策最近變得「非常可預測」，通膨率和基準借貸成本均位於2%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，歐洲央行自6月以來一直維持利率不變，投資者和經濟學家目前均預計該行不會有進一步行動。法國央行行長Francois Villeroy de Galhau周二早些時候接受彭博電視採訪時稱，任何新關稅都須進行評估，但補充道他預計其對價格的影響「有限」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德強調，美歐之間的貿易聯繫「非常緊密」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「危及這一點，質疑這一點，對良好的商業政策無益，」她指出。「美國企業應該像歐洲企業一樣，認真思考這個問題。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB’s Lagarde Says Uncertainty Is Back Amid Latest Trump Threats</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E6%8B%89%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B7%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E4%BB%A4%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E6%8D%B2%E5%9C%9F%E9%87%8D%E4%BE%86-232854848.html",
