        {
            "title": "瑞銀：拋售美國資產是危險的賭博 把配置完全轉移出美國是不可能的",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"瑞銀：拋售美國資產是危險的賭博 把配置完全轉移出美國是不可能的\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JoFBYe_k0LwjgYGQwWgFrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/8b275670-f66b-11f0-b7af-f8751dfe3b03\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">瑞銀：拋售美國資產是危險的賭博 把配置完全轉移出美國是不可能的</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80-%E6%8B%8B%E5%94%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E6%98%AF%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E6%8A%8A%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E7%9A%84-175347871.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 09:54:36",
