        {
            "title": "日本國債拋售風暴波及海外 財相承諾採取措施並喊話市場「冷靜」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"日本國債拋售風暴波及海外 財相承諾採取措施並喊話市場「冷靜」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0CxkO4sncSdw.Jo9l4VElw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/dc622170-f65f-11f0-bff7-a8dfbcbb36a2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">日本國債拋售風暴波及海外 財相承諾採取措施並喊話市場「冷靜」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
