        {
            "title": "零食商鳴鳴很忙IPO籌33億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"內地零食連鎖零售商鳴鳴很忙將於周五截止招股。（網上圖片）\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IRn5wCSGcw58lbsOjrfgnA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/c83dfac0-f65a-11f0-baff-e101d22f172b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">內地零食連鎖零售商鳴鳴很忙將於周五截止招股。（網上圖片）</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國零食連鎖零售商鳴鳴很忙（1768.HK）昨日啟動招股，計劃集資最多33.36億元，並引入騰訊（0700.HK）、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:淡馬錫;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/淡馬錫\">淡馬錫</a>等8名基石投資者坐鎮。首日招股券商暫為其借出409.94億元孖展，以公開發售集資額3.34億元計，相當於超購逾121倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>騰訊淡馬錫為基投 23899元入場</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鳴鳴很忙周五（23日）截止招股，發售1410.11萬股H股，香港公開發售佔10%，不設強制回撥；每股招股價介乎229.6元至236.6元，一手100股，入場費23898.62元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-da8b11a0-1520-3bbd-b755-3425bf21a1bb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該股預期1月28日掛牌，高盛和華泰國際為保薦人；上市預期市值料達491.58億至506.56億元。另交易設有10%發售量調整權和15%超額配股權。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鳴鳴很忙引入了8名基石投資者認購1.95億美元（約15.2億港元）等值股份，按招股價上限計，相當於基本發售規模45.55%。基投陣容包括騰訊、淡馬錫、貝萊德、富達基金、博時國際、易方達、Springs Capital（Hong Kong）和泰康人壽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>大族數控通過上市聆訊</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該企計劃把集資所得約25%用於提升供應鏈能力及提高產品開發能力；約20%用於店舖網絡升級，以及加盟商的持續賦能；約20%用於品牌建設及推廣活動；約20%用於提升科技能力和數字化水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，PCB專用生產設備解決方案服務商大族數控（301200.SZ）已通過港交所（0388.HK）上市聆訊，中金公司為保薦人。IFR報道，大族數控已展開上市前推介，計劃籌集5億至8億美元（約39億至62.4億港元）。按其A股周二收市價計，市值為572.1億元。</p></div>",
